Study format:

online, (a)synchronous depending on group availability.

Expectations form participants:: 

Learners will take part in the following activities:  

1. discussions; 

2. surveys; 

3. simulations of interviews; 

4. presentations; 

5. an interview conducted by an HR expert/recruiter or university career advisor

Evaluation will be based on: 

1. continuous assessment; 

2. self- and peer-evaluation; 

3. pitch presentation.
